            "name": "Drench",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The wisp puts out all fires in a single 5-foot square. They extinguish non-magical fire of that size or smaller automatically and attempt to counteract magical fires (counteract modifier +6).",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
